A. n + m <= x < 2n and 2m <= y <= n + m
B. n + m <= x < 2n and 2m <= y <= 2n
C. 2m <= x < 2n and 2m <= y <= n + m
D. 2m <= x <= 2n and 2m <= y <= 2n

